items.title: Wyoming GOP Sen. Lummis will not run for reelection
items.description: Sen. Cynthia Lummis, Wyoming Republican, announced Friday that she will not run for reelection in 2026, citing a "change of heart."

items.title: Rep. Elise Stefanik drops out of New York's governor race, no reelection bid for House
items.description: Rep. Elise Stefanik has suspended her campaign for New York governorand said she will not be seeking reelection for her House seat, either.
